Package com.epoch.evals

Classes for calling and retrieving data from evaluators.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    EvalInterface
    Interface for implementing all evaluators.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CombineExpr
    Methods for combining evaluators or rules on permissible synthetic starting materials.
    EvalManager
    Manages and interfaces with the various classes that actually evaluate responses.
    EvalResult
    Holds a response, and usually the result of its evaluation.
    Evaluator
    A generalized evaluator, with methods for submitting a response for evaluation and combining subevaluators' results into a single result to pass back to the front end.
    OneEvalResult
    Holds the result of the evaluation of a response by a single evaluator.
    Subevaluator
    Contains the information needed to instantiate an evaluator implementation that actually does the work of evaluating a response.
